</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/16ee950683349dacdd9e9c262ff6133812747edd" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:9.777ex; height:2.176ex;" alt="\nabla \cdot \mathbf {B} =0"/></span><span about="#mwt589">
</span></p></td>
<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:99%; border:none; padding:0.08em;">
