</span> are the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Vector_field" title="Vector field" id="mwAok">vector fields</a> of the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Electric_Field" title="Electric Field" id="mwAoo" class="mw-redirect">Electric Field</a> (measured in <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Volt" title="Volt" id="mwAos">V</a>/<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Meter" title="Meter" id="mwAow" class="mw-redirect">m</a> or <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Newtons" title="Newtons" id="mwAo0" class="mw-redirect">N</a>/<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Coulomb" title="Coulomb" id="mwAo4">C</a>) and the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Magnetic_Field" title="Magnetic Field" id="mwAo8" class="mw-redirect">Magnetic Field</a> (measured in <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Tesla_(unit)" title="Tesla (unit)" id="mwApA">T</a> or <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Weber_(unit)" title="Weber (unit)" id="mwApE">Wb</a>/<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Square_meter" title="Square meter" id="mwApI" class="mw-redirect">m<sup id="mwApM">2</sup></a>), respectively;</dd>
<dd id="mwApQ"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt530" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"\\nabla \\cdot X "}}' id="mwApU"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \nabla \cdot X}">
