</span> are <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Partial_derivatives" title="Partial derivatives" id="mwAp0" class="mw-redirect">partial derivatives</a> (rate of change in time, with location fixed) of the magnetic and electric field;</dd>
<dd id="mwAp4"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt540" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"\\mu_0"}}' id="mwAp8"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \mu _{0}}">
  <semantics>
