</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/75ee4610a644d1b4e038ff152ef47f067925f722" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:2.811ex; height:2.509ex;" alt="\mathbf {E} _{0}"/></span><span about="#mwt457">
</span> is the constant amplitude, <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt562" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"f"}}' id="mwAvU"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle f}">
