</span> is any second differentiable function, <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt459" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":" \\hat{\\mathbf{k}}"}}' id="mwAvY"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle {\hat {\mathbf {k} }}}">
