</span> is a unit vector in the direction of propagation, and <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt461" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":" {\\mathbf{x}} "}}' id="mwAvc"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle {\mathbf {x} }}">
