25" id="mwA2c"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt25" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwA2g"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-10" id="cite_note-10"><a href="./Electromagnetic_radiation#cite_ref-10" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-10" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt26" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Cite web","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"http://www.clerkmaxwellfoundation.org/html/maxwell-s_impact_.html"},"title":{"wt":"The Impact of James Clerk Maxwell&apos;s Work"},"website":{"wt":"www.clerkmaxwellfoundation.org"},"access-date":{"wt":"2017-09-04"},"deadurl":{"wt":"no"},"archiveurl":{"wt":"https://web.archive.org/web/20170917213509/http://www.clerkmaxwellfoundation.org/html/maxwell-s_impact_.html"},"archivedate":{"wt":"17 September 2017"},"df":{"wt":"dmy-all"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwA2k"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.clerkmaxwellfoundation.org/html/maxwell-s_impact_.html" id="mwA2o">"The Impact of James Clerk Maxwell's Work"</a>. <i id="mwA2s">www.clerkmaxwellfoundation.org</i>. <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20170917213509/http://www.clerkmaxwellfoundation.org/html/maxwell-s_impact_.html" id="mwA2w">Archived</a> from the original on 17 September 2017<span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwA20">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwA24">4 September</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=www.clerkmaxwellfoundation.org&amp;rft.atitle=The+Impact+of+James+Clerk+Maxwell%27s+Work&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clerkmaxwellfoundation.org%2Fhtml%2Fmax